HOME_DELIVERY.pricing: 4 EUR for orders under 70 EUR. Free for orders over 70 EUR.
HOME_DELIVERY.delivery_time: Naručene artikle kurirska služba dostavlja u roku od 8 radnih dana. Tijekom akcija, moguć je duži rok isporuke.

SUMMARY: DELIVERY OPTIONS: Home delivery is the only option available. PROVIDERS: GLS is the exclusive courier. PRICING: Delivery costs €4 for orders below €70 and is free for orders of €70 or more. DELIVERY TIME: Standard delivery takes up to 8 working days, with possible delays during sales periods. PAYMENT: The only payment method is cash on delivery (pouzeće). NOTABLE FEATURES: There is no express or weekend delivery. No information is provided regarding surcharges for island deliveries. In-store pickup is not available for online orders. Returns sent via Hrvatska Pošta (HP) are not accepted. WEBSITE ASSESSMENT: Shipping information is found within the 'Uvjeti poslovanja' (Terms of Business) page. The information is basic but clear. It lacks details on island delivery and alternative shipping methods, which would improve completeness.
